card.name: Invigorated Assault
card.text: For each kind of counter on target creature you control, put another counter of that kind on it or remove one from it. Then it deals damage equal to its power to target creature you don't control.

card.name: Bitter Chill Bravery
card.text: Target creature gets +3/+3 until end of turn. If {S} was spent to cast this spell, instead put three +1/+1 counters on that creature. ({S} is mana from a snow source.)

card.name: Hyperfrost
card.text: Enchant land When this Aura enters, draw a card. Enchanted land is snow in addition to its other types and has "{T}: Add {C}{C}."

card.name: Grapple with the Past
card.text: Mill three cards, then you may return a creature or land card from your graveyard to your hand. (To mill three cards, put the top three cards of your library into your graveyard.)

card.name: Preprogrammed Guide
card.text: When this creature enters or dies, surveil 1. (Look at the top card of your library. You may put it into your graveyard.)

card.name: Rustwing Wayfinder
card.text: Flying Whenever this creature attacks, put up to one target card from a graveyard on the bottom of its owner's library.

card.name: Stormbound Walker
card.text: This creature enters tapped. When it enters, surveil 1. (Look at the top card of your library. You may put it into your graveyard.) When this creature dies, create a Splinter token. (It's a snow artifact with "{T}, Sacrifice this artifact: Add {C}.")

card.name: Perilous Icicle
card.text: {4}{S}, {T} or {7}, {T}, Sacrifice this artifact: Destroy target nonland permanent. ({S} is mana from a snow source.)

card.name: Frozen Wardsphere
card.text: This artifact enters tapped. {1}, {T}: Add one mana of any color. {T}, Sacrifice this artifact: Surveil 1, then draw a card. (To surveil 1, look at the top card of your library. You may put it into your graveyard.)

card.name: Fresh Rations
card.text: Whenever equipped creature attacks, it gets +2/+2 until end of turn. Untap it. Equip—Sacrifice a creature. (Sacrifice a creature: Attach to target creature you control. Equip only as a sorcery.)

card.name: Unfathomable Chasm
card.text: {T}, Sacrifice this land: Search your library for a basic land card, put it onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle. {T}, Sacrifice this land: Create a Splinter token. (It's a snow artifact with "{T}, Sacrifice this artifact: Add {C}.")

card.text: Flying

card.name: God's Embrace GOD
card.text: At the beginning of each opponent's upkeep, if that player has one or fewer cards in hand, they lose 2 life and you gain 2 life.
